{
  "texts": [
    "This is done in our paper.",
    "The goal of this paper is further similar to HELM in the intend to use the same benchmarks on all considered models instead of a sparse evaluation matrix of tests and models.",
    "Besides that, the evaluation in this paper has only a small overlap in models considered (e.g., T0pp and T5) and proposes own tests instead of reusing the popular ones.",
    "The evaluation of LLMs in [2] does a good job of summarizing developments of the last years but is not concerned with own benchmark results.",
    "Mahowald et al. [24]analyze LLMs from a linguistic perspective and differentiate between formal and functional linguistic competences."
  ]
}